"Change the thickness of the slab by :guilabel:`Width / Cell` in "
":guilabel:`Slab System` and the thickness of the vacuum layer by "
":guilabel:`Width / Angs.` in :guilabel:`Vacuum of a Side`\\ . Enter the "
"repeat count in the text boxes in :guilabel:`Area Scaling` and click "
